PROJECT DETAILS / PROJEKTDETAILS:
- Name: SQLite Admin Dashboard
- Repository: https://github.com/ochtii/sqlite-admin-dashboard
- Author: ochtii
- Technology Stack: React.js, Express.js, SQLite3, Node.js
- Purpose: Database administration tool with modern UI and authentication

